{"tid":2137273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍陸戰隊訓練遇難8人失蹤多日 軍方宣布停止搜救","createTime":"2020-08-02T21:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T20:31:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f6eda3a1a9644c1b23fcd994786f7c248550baee","tid":2137273,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T21:45:53.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/08/02 22:01<br />\n<br />\n（中央社洛杉磯2日綜合外電報導）美軍陸戰隊幾天前在加州附近海域發生事故，軍方今天宣布停止搜尋下落不明的7名陸戰隊員和1名水手，並認定他們已經殉職。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n第15陸戰遠征隊指揮官布朗齊（Christopher Bronzi）說：「我帶著沉重的心情，決定結束搜救行動。」<br />\n<br />\n陸戰隊透過聲明表示，軍方出動陸戰隊、海軍與海岸防衛隊直升機、船艦，歷經40小時搜救，一共找了超過1000平方海里的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n布朗齊表示，現在將把行動目的從搜救改成尋找失蹤者遺體。（譯者：楊昭彥/核稿：林治平）1090802<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202008020213.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202008020213.aspx&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=90ec9e94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202008020213.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"2c1788eb5bbfbcb3c088f81b8c6cb2e7227b19d4","tid":2137273,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T21:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3336c610d38c3bf65cfd20e99cd7bde05ec902","tid":2137273,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T22:01:08.000Z","msg":"遇到ufo 又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689b64a29a757a8e30ddf13dc027cf5aa2b2aaeb","tid":2137273,"uid":199957,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T22:28:19.000Z","msg":"諗起上年直升機嗰單<br />\n支那個邊直接救都費事救 仲要掩蓋消息"},{"pid":"e6e7eb08ea2186fdac8643245e82e5eeb3c5267f","tid":2137273,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T23:14:06.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d774f25ac4a